                            </h2>
                            <label
                                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full h-16 px-5 border border-slate-200 border-dashed rounded-xl cursor-pointer bg-surface-50 hover:bg-surface-100 hover:border-navy-900 transition group"
                                id="upload-area">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3" id="upload-placeholder">
                                    <i data-lucide="upload-cloud"
                                        class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-navy-900 transition-colors"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">Unggah foto bukti</p>
